high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the sofa on your right.
Pick up potato from the sofa.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the microwave.
Put potato inside the oven and heat it and then take it out.
Turn around and walk to the dining table to your left.
Place potato on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Heating a potato into microwave and place it on dining table.
